        </div>
        <span class="disp" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:800">StudySync</span>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size:11.5px;color:var(--t3);letter-spacing:.03em">Section‑G · CSE AI&ML · JNTUH R25</p>
